
1. Proxy setting
   1. Close any running IntelliJ IDEA instances
   1. Add this line to your idea.properties file:
    java.net.useSystemProxies=true
   1. Start IntelliJ, go to File – Settings – HTTP Proxy, select "Auto-detect proxy settings"
1. Maven proxy setting
   <proxy>
      <id>astrill</id>
      <active>true</active>
      <protocol>https</protocol>
      <host>127.0.0.1</host>
      <port>8281</port><!-- check your own proxy server port from system proxy settings -->
    </proxy>
